          <p><hi rend="italic">Subscriptions may be paid</hi> to Mr J. W. <hi rend="smallCaps">Clark</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Trinity College, 
                or to his account with Messrs</hi> <hi rend="smallCaps">Mortlock</hi>.<ref target="#foot.f15"/></p>
    </div>
